Definition: washing out the stomach with sterile water or a saltwater solution
Example: removes blood or poisons; when the doctor ordered a gastric lavage the hospital pumped out my stomach
Synonyms: lavage, washing, out, the, stomach, with, sterile, water, or, a, saltwater, solution, removes, blood, poisons, when, doctor, ordered, gastric, hospital, pumped, my
Category: noun.act
